    <mads:note type="source">Brill's New Pauly: "Arrian, 3, Anonymus author of a Periplus Ponti Euxini, 
        Term for the anonymous author of one Periplus Ponti Euxini which is primarily based on the  Periplus of 
        Menippus in the epitome of Marcianus, the Periplus of  Arrianus [2], Ps.  Scymnus and Ps. Scylax;
        probably written after AD 576...."Badian, Ernst (Cambridge, MA) and Heucke, Clemens (Munich), “Arrianus”,
